Vice President Joe Biden has issued a statement regarding the departure of his deputy chief of staff, Alan Hoffman. Biden praises Hoffman as a trusted advisor and highlights his leadership, intelligence, and loyalty. Hoffman has played a crucial role in managing Biden's staff and has been dedicated to strengthening law enforcement, advocating for the labor community, and building a strong middle class. Biden expresses his respect and admiration for Hoffman, acknowledging his contributions and wishing him the best. The vice president believes that Hoffman's wisdom, experience, and passion will be greatly missed.